brief_summary.textblock: There will be breast tissue changes after use of a breast pump.

clinical_study.brief_title: Breast Tissue Before And After Breastfeeding Or The Use Of A Breast Pump
condition: To Collect Measurements of the Nipple
To Record Clinical Observations of the Nipple, Areola, and Breast Tissue Before and After Breastfeeding
To Record Clinical Observations of the Nipple, Areola, and Breast Tissue Before and After Expressing Milk With 3 Different Electric Breast Pumps.

criteria.textblock:
Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Lactating women who were breastfeeding.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Non breastfeeding or non lactating women.

primary_outcome.description: Lactating women used a 1 of 3 breast pumps or breastfed for 10 minutes.
